Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.95,0:01:00.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}月亮轻声低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:06.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}用无人听到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.25,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}编织潮涨潮落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:14.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}记忆中的景色无法消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)}繁星密集地标记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:24.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}用无人理解的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}无限的语言卷成漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.44,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}孕育出千亿本书
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.91,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}天空对我太宽广
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}时间对我太迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}一无所知地空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}聚集的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}也只会在土地中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:06.68,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}即便如此我仍喊叫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}莫名地提高声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:16.99,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}至少要响彻天的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:22.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,400,3000,4000)}太阳会因此升起吧


Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.23,0:00:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 快救救我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是算了 我遵守和你的约定

